Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Boney Peak
Description: One of the highest peaks in the Santa Monica Mountains, overlooking Newbury Park, CA

Name: Kayangan Lake
Description: Dubbed the "cleanest lake in Asia," the lake is one of the Philippines' most picturesque locations

Name: Emerald Bay State Park
Description: A Natural National Landmark located on the southwest corner of Lake Tahoe, CA.  It features the only island in the lake, Fannette Island.

Name: Augusta National Golf Club
Description: Famous for its impeccable groundskeeping and beautiful vegetation, this golf course is home to the annual Masters golf tournament (the only of the 4 PGA Tour Major Championships to be held at the same location annually).

Name: Grand Place
Description: The central square of Brussels, Belgium, surrounded by opulent Baroque guildhalls, a town hall, and a museum.  It is a popular tourist destination and has various restaurants and shops surrounding the area.
